            {
              "text": "I'm baking a birthday cake for my dad this weekend. He likes coffee flavours.",
              "type": "text",
            },
          ],
          "createdAt": "2026-06-25T19:40:07.882064Z",
          "files": [],
          "id": "a3c5e7f9-1b4d-4c6e-8a0b-2d5f7a9c1e36",
          "parentId": null,
          "sender": "human",
          "updatedAt": "2026-06-25T19:40:07.882064Z",
        },
        {
          "attachments": [],
          "blocks": [
            {
              "text": "A classic **coffee and walnut cake** would be perfect — two sponge layers flavoured with strong espresso, filled and topped with coffee buttercream and walnut halves. Want the full recipe?",
              "type": "text",
            },
          ],
          "createdAt": "2026-06-25T19:40:12.550317Z",
          "files": [],
          "id": "b6d8f0a2-4c7e-4d9b-a1c3-5e8f0b2d4a67",
          "parentId": "a3c5e7f9-1b4d-4c6e-8a0b-2d5f7a9c1e36",
          "sender": "assistant",
          "updatedAt": "2026-06-25T19:40:41.209864Z",
        },
        {
          "attachments": [],
          "blocks": [
            {
              "text": "Yes, give me the recipe for an 8-inch tin.",
              "type": "text",
            },
          ],
          "createdAt": "2026-06-25T19:41:29.774052Z",
          "files": [],
          "id": "c9b1d3e5-6f8a-4b0c-9d2e-4a7c9e1f3b50",
          "parentId": "b6d8f0a2-4c7e-4d9b-a1c3-5e8f0b2d4a67",
          "sender": "human",
          "updatedAt": "2026-06-25T19:41:29.774052Z",
        },
        {
          "attachments": [],
          "blocks": [
            {
              "text": "**Coffee & walnut cake (8-inch)**

Sponge: 225 g butter, 225 g caster sugar, 4 eggs, 225 g self-raising flour, 2 tbsp espresso, 75 g chopped walnuts. Bake 25 min at 180°C.

Buttercream: 125 g butter, 250 g icing sugar, 1 tbsp espresso.",
              "type": "text",
            },
          ],
          "createdAt": "2026-06-25T19:41:34.918263Z",
          "files": [],
          "id": "d2f4b6c8-0a3e-4c5d-b7f9-6b9e1d3f5c74",
