          },
        ],
        "createdAt": "2026-06-25T19:40:12.550317Z",
        "files": [],
        "id": "b6d8f0a2-4c7e-4d9b-a1c3-5e8f0b2d4a67",
        "parentId": "a3c5e7f9-1b4d-4c6e-8a0b-2d5f7a9c1e36",
        "sender": "assistant",
        "updatedAt": "2026-06-25T19:40:41.209864Z",
      },
      {
        "attachments": [],
        "blocks": [
          {
            "text": "Actually he can't eat nuts — can you make it coffee-only, for an 8-inch tin?",
            "type": "text",
          },
        ],
        "createdAt": "2026-06-25T19:50:44.287930Z",
        "files": [],
        "id": "f8c0a2d4-5e7b-4a9c-8b1d-3c6e8a0d2f45",
        "parentId": "b6d8f0a2-4c7e-4d9b-a1c3-5e8f0b2d4a67",
        "sender": "human",
        "updatedAt": "2026-06-25T19:50:44.287930Z",
      },
      {
        "attachments": [],
        "blocks": [
          {
            "text": "No problem — skip the walnuts entirely.

**Coffee cake (8-inch, nut-free)**

Sponge: 225 g butter, 225 g caster sugar, 4 eggs, 225 g self-raising flour, 3 tbsp espresso. Bake 25 min at 180°C.

Buttercream: 125 g butter, 250 g icing sugar, 1½ tbsp espresso. Decorate with chocolate-coated coffee beans instead of walnut halves.",
            "type": "text",
          },
        ],
        "createdAt": "2026-06-25T19:50:49.902174Z",
        "files": [],
        "id": "e5a7c9b1-3d6f-4e8a-b2c4-7f0d2b4e6a83",
        "parentId": "f8c0a2d4-5e7b-4a9c-8b1d-3c6e8a0d2f45",
        "sender": "assistant",
        "updatedAt": "2026-06-25T19:52:33.410975Z",
      },
    ],
    "source": "chat",
    "summary": "",
    "title": "Birthday cake ideas",
    "updatedAt": "2026-06-25T19:52:33.410975Z",
  },
  "issues": [],
}
`;

